msgid ""
":class:`Gtk.FileChooserDialog` inherits from :class:`Gtk.Dialog`, so buttons "
"have response IDs such as :attr:`Gtk.ResponseType.ACCEPT` and :attr:`Gtk."
"ResponseType.CANCEL` which can be specified in the :class:`Gtk."
